874:// applyFailingLBLocked is akin to configuring an LB policy on the channel which
875:// always fails RPCs. Here, an actual LB policy is not configured, but an always
876:// erroring picker is configured, which returns errors with information about
877:// what was invalid in the received service config. A config selector with no
